Hatebase,is,an,international,repository,of,multilingual,structured,usage,based,hate,speech,The,database,was,developed,to,help,government,agencies,NGOs,and,other,organizations,use,hate,speech,as,a,predictor,for,regional,violence,The,Hatebase,API,provides,authorized,users,with,developer,access,to,Hatebase,data,Supported,queries,include,data,on,vocabulary,and,sightings,The,read,only,API,returns,XML,or,JSON,formatted,responses